wdi-GC.XPN.GSRV.CN.def: Goods and services include all government payments in exchange for goods and services used for the production of market and nonmarket goods and services. Own-account capital formation is excluded.
wdi-GC.XPN.GSRV.CN.name: Goods and services expense
wdi-GC.XPN.GSRV.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
